@startuml
title Query Loop 主循环

skinparam backgroundColor #F7F1E6
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 135
skinparam ranksep 40
skinparam nodesep 26
skinparam defaultFontName Georgia
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam TitleFontSize 20
skinparam NoteFontSize 14
skinparam ArrowFontSize 13
skinparam TitleFontColor #161616
skinparam ArrowColor #5E5A53
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #1D1D1D
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #F2E9D9
skinparam RectangleFontColor #161616
skinparam RectangleRoundCorner 10
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #F5EBDD
  BorderColor #8C2721
  FontColor #7B1E1E
}

left to right direction

rectangle "Turn Start" as start_turn #E8DDD0
rectangle "Prepare turn context\nprefetch / boundary / budget /\nsnip / microcompact" as prepare #F2E9D9
rectangle "Blocking check" as blocking #F5EBDD
rectangle "Model streaming" as model #EFE6D8
rectangle "Tool execution\nStreamingToolExecutor" as tools #EFE6D8
rectangle "Append turn effects" as effects #F2E9D9
rectangle "Stop hooks" as stop_hooks #F2E9D9
rectangle "Terminal" as terminal #E8DDD0
rectangle "Surface error" as error_box #F5EBDD

start_turn --> prepare
prepare --> blocking
blocking --> error_box : limit hit
blocking --> model : ok
model --> tools : tool_use
model --> effects : no tool_use
tools --> effects : tool results merged
effects --> start_turn : follow-up / next turn
effects --> stop_hooks : stable completion
stop_hooks --> terminal
error_box --> terminal

note right
主循环负责：
- 输入治理
- 模型调用
- 工具回填
- 下一轮重入
end note

@enduml
